# Local environment overrides for release checks.
#
# Copy to .env (git-ignored) only if you need local overrides or emergency
# local PyPI upload. Normal release publishing uses the GitHub Actions
# `pypi` environment secret named PYPI_API_TOKEN.
#
# Example:
# CALIPER_SMOKE_ALLOW_NETWORK=0
# TWINE_USERNAME=__token__
# TWINE_PASSWORD=pypi-replace-me
# PYPI_API_TOKEN=pypi-replace-me
